code: /**  * Test that schedule modes set the lazy deployment flag correctly.  */ @Test public void testAllowLazyDeployment() throws Exception {     assertTrue(ScheduleMode.LAZY_FROM_SOURCES.allowLazyDeployment()).     assertFalse(ScheduleMode.EAGER.allowLazyDeployment()). }
